Package pt.iade.dsm.controllers

Class AdoptionPopUpController

java.lang.Object
pt.iade.dsm.controllers.AdoptionPopUpController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class AdoptionPopUpController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
This class is the controller for the adoption pop up on the guest's page where the information and the behavior of the interface get manipulated. Its a pop-up where the guest requests a dog, already chosen.
